snippet.textDisplay:
I mean, Matt's work is always amazing, but I think this is some of his best work. Shroud just oozed the perfect combination of charisma, menace, control and intelligence to me.

Edit: I also have to give massive props to the writing, visual and audio design teams. Performance can only take you so far with bad material, but the red smoke, creepy mask eye, and audio stings were perfect.
